## Supabase Schema

### `users`
| column | type | notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid pk | |
| email | text unique | |
| credits | int | default 0 |
| created_at | timestamp | |

### `jobs`
| column | type | notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid pk | |
| user_email | text | |
| status | text | queued/processing/completed/failed |
| input_type | text | url/deck/both |
| input_url | text | |
| input_company_name | text | |
| report_storage_path | text | Supabase Storage path |
| total_cost_usd | decimal | |
| error_message | text | |
| created_at | timestamp | |
| started_at | timestamp | |
| completed_at | timestamp | |

### `api_calls`
| column | type | notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid pk | |
| job_id | uuid → jobs | |
| provider | text | openai/gemini/exa/mailersend |
| model | text | |
| endpoint | text | |
| pipeline_step | text | step-0 through step-7 |
| system_prompt | text | |
| user_prompt | text | |
| response | text | |
| input_tokens | int | |
| output_tokens | int | |
| cost_usd | decimal | |
| latency_ms | int | |
| created_at | timestamp | |

### `models`
| column | type | notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid pk | |
| provider | text | |
| model_id | text unique | |
| display_name | text | |
| input_cost_per_1m_usd | decimal | |
| output_cost_per_1m_usd | decimal | |
| context_window_tokens | int | |
| enabled | bool | |
| deprecated_at | timestamp | |
| notes | text | |

**Seeded models (March 2026):**
- `gemini-2.5-pro`: $1.25/$10.00 per 1M
- `gemini-2.5-flash`: $0.30/$2.50 per 1M ← synthesis default
- `gemini-2.5-flash-lite`: $0.10/$0.40 per 1M ← extraction default
- `gemini-2.0-flash`: $0.10/$0.40 ⚠️ deprecated June 1 2026
- `gpt-4o-mini`: $0.15/$0.60 per 1M
- `gpt-4o`: $2.50/$10.00 per 1M

### `pipeline_config`
Key/value pairs editable from admin dashboard:

| key | default | description |
|-----|---------|-------------|
| exa_find_similar_results | 20 | Max results per findSimilar call |
| exa_competitor_layers | 2 | Layers of competitor search |
| exa_layer1_max_competitors | 5 | Top N passed to Layer 2 |
| exa_max_competitors_total | 15 | Max unique competitors to enrich |
| synthesis_model | gemini-2.5-flash | Model ID for report synthesis |
| extraction_model | gemini-2.5-flash-lite | Model for company extraction |
| gap_analysis_enabled | true | Whether to run gap analysis |
| gap_analysis_model | gemini-2.5-flash-lite | Model for gap analysis |
| gap_analysis_max_rounds | 1 | Max gap analysis rounds |
| max_context_tokens | 100000 | Max tokens fed into synthesis |

### `prompts`
All prompts editable from admin dashboard:

| key | description |
|-----|-------------|
| extraction_system | System prompt for company info extraction |
| extraction_user | User prompt template for extraction |
| description_generation_system | Prompt for generating keyword descriptions |
| synthesis_system | System prompt for report synthesis |
| synthesis_user | User prompt template ({{variables}}) |
| gap_analysis_system | System prompt for gap analysis |
| gap_analysis_user | User prompt template |

