## Admin Dashboard Pages

Served directly from the Railway Express app (no separate Vercel needed):
- `/` — Overview: recent jobs, cost today/month, error rate, active users
- `/jobs` — Job list, filterable by status/date
- `/jobs/:id` — Full job detail: pipeline timeline, every API call with prompts/responses/costs
- `/users` — CRUD: email, credits, usage history
- `/models` — Model table: pricing, enabled/disabled toggle, add new models
- `/config` — Pipeline config key/value editor (all pipeline_config rows)
- `/prompts` — All system + user prompt templates, editable
- `/test` — Submit a URL → triggers a job → sends PDF to dagnytaggart1997@gmail.com

